&lt;li&gt;Working familiarity with data-collection instrumentation (specific instruments are coachable on the job)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical aptitude and a demonstrated ability to learn new test methods quickly&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Careful, organized approach to high-throughput testing while maintaining high data quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
