&lt;li&gt;Coding: Python, C++, Arduino&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Microcontroller work (demonstrates familiarity with circuitry, PCBs, and firmware flashing)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Soldering experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data analysis skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience in a hardware test/reliability lab&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High d

