&lt;li&gt;Track changing environmental and safety regulations across two sites and, with guidance and oversight from the EHS Lead, translate new requirements into site-specific programs and corrective actions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with engineers and scientists to ensure their processes are safe, and review new and existing chemicals&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
