&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience within a health and safety role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience handling, storing, safekeeping, and removing hazardous materials (e.g., acids, bases, solvents)&lt;/li&gt;
